Theme/Base V2 1.5.1

	* Upgrade the bundled versions of jQuery to 2.1.1 and jQueryUI to 1.11.2
	* Remove the icheckbox jquery plugin from base-v2, (it should have never been there in the first
	  place).
	* Slightly different output from the SASS compiler.
	* Page published_expires had a value set on form submission because MySQL *always* parses int fields
	  to 0 if null or empty is sent...regardless if the field allows null.
	* Include the viewport scale metatag by default.
	* Do not have a margin on navigation ULs.
	* Include the .map files in base-v2 theme metafile.
	* Decrease the min-width on minict select elements.
	-- Charlie Powell <charlie@eval.bz>  Fri, 21 Nov 2014 16:52:22 -0500

